<br>
Open your character ini, it should look something like<br>
<br>
YourName_51<br>
<br>
Scroll down til you see your hotkey bank, it will look like<br>
<br>
Page1Button1Name=HairINC<br>
Page1Button1Color=0<br>
Page1Button1Line1=/gsay Enter musical symbols here (or others that you wish)<br>
<br>
And save the file.  It's a good idea to make a backup beforehand just in case something goes wrong.  It's also worth the mention that this <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>is</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> frowned upon by Sony/EQ and if you were to be petitioned, or use in the zone with a GM - you're likely to get a warning and asked not to use this function in the future.<br>
<br>
Anywho, hope the explanation covers what you need.  If not let me know and I'll try to give a better instructions.<br>
<br>
